claim.claim-text:
1. A portable work station comprising: 
a luggage carrier having a handle; 
a support member having a first portion, a second portion and a hinge interconnecting said first and second portions, said second portion being movable relative to said first portion between a closed position wherein said first and second portions are arranged in a facing relationship and an open position wherein said first and second surfaces are arranged in a side-by-side relationship to form a generally planer work surface; 
a clamping mechanism releasably securing said support member to said handle; and 
an leg pivotally coupled to said first portion, said leg being movable relative to said first portion between a stowed portion wherein said leg is adjacent said support member and an extended position wherein said leg extends away from said support member.
